					<span class="label"><a name="footnote14-13291_002_043">14.</a></span>
					<p class="">Gordon B. Hinckley, &ldquo;<a href="http://www.lds.org/general-conference/1995/04/this-is-the-work-of-the-master?lang=spa">&Eacute;sta es la obra del Maestro</a>&rdquo;, <span class="emphasis">Liahona</span>, julio de 1995, p&aacute;gs. 80&ndash;81.</p>
